name: Graffiti Tags - 001
description: This image titled "Graffiti" is the first one of a series of an ongoing research project called "The Amazing Augmented Tagger Machine", which explores the joint development of graffiti tags by a person and a machine. The project employs machine learning (ML, pix2pix) to generate novel street tags that transcend traditional letter forms. The writer is able to generate her own ML graffiti tags in the ghostly belly of a deep convolution neural network and later transfer them to a real surface using
